nodes.text: This unidentified bounty hunter captured Dova Brigger who had a bounty placed on her and her brother by the leader of the Smugglers' Confederation Nirama.
A unidentified bounty hunter captured Dova Brigger, who had a bounty placed on her and her brother, by the leader of the Smugglers' Confederation Nirama.
The unidentified bounty hunter was first mention in James Luceno's novel Millennium Falcon, which was released on October 21, 2008.
